ckquote>同一件事到底要講幾多次</blockquote><br />\n你睇下出面都有好多巴打對同一件時事出post表達自己意見，亦有不同巴打講話自己帽咗等等...但我覺得每個人都有自己獨特嘅故事，如果講到你覺得煩嘅咁對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d95a2a734d577bbc6f9980966764289900d50e","tid":391522,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44ccd9339790a52139d283c629878054f73e18b","tid":391522,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}